            "customization_block_heading": "CUSTOM MILLWORK",
            "customization_block_desc": "<p>Custom-built counters, cabinets, and display units designed to fit your space perfectly, elevate your brand, and create a polished, professional look that builds trust and improves the customer experience.</p>"
